parameters.name: ClusterId
parameters.description: The ID of the master instance.

parameters.name: Force
parameters.description:
Specifies whether to forcefully delete the master instance in ACK One. Valid values:

*   true: forcefully deletes the master instance in ACK One.
*   false: does not forcibly delete the master instance in ACK One.

Default value: false.

parameters.name: RetainResources
parameters.description: The list of resources to retain.
